title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: Exception occurs in ReportEngineService.getMetaData() when exporting data from a table that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
EB: Exporting the data from the table should successfully result in the data being exported without any exceptions.
SR: Steps to reproduce: 1. Add a table to the report with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 2. Preview the attached report. 3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
